38-2524.Fees.

The department shall establish and collect fees for credentialing activities under the Occupational Therapy Practice Act as provided in sections 38-151 to 38-157.

SourceLaws 1984, LB 761, § 42;Laws 1986, LB 926, § 63;Laws 1988, LB 1100, § 177;Laws 1992, LB 1019, § 92;Laws 1994, LB 1223, § 78;Laws 2003, LB 242, § 143;R.S.1943, (2003), § 71-6114;Laws 2007, LB463, § 864.
